---
name: audio-transcribe
description: Transcribe audio files (ogg, mp3, wav) to text using local OpenAI Whisper. Use this skill when the user sends a voice note or audio file that needs to be understood.
---

# Audio Transcribe

Uses a local installation of OpenAI Whisper to transcribe audio files.

## Usage

```bash
~/opt/whisper/bin/python ~/opt/openclaw/skills/audio-transcribe/transcribe.py <path_to_audio_file>
```

## Setup

Requires a python venv at `~/opt/whisper` with `openai-whisper` and `ffmpeg-python` installed.
System must have `ffmpeg` installed.
